<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV69">
<l>kāṇilummu ruppolārce vikkiṉāta kīrttiyār</l>
<l>pēṇilumva rantarami ṭukkilāta tēvarai</l>
<l>yāṇameṉṟa ṭaintuvāḻu mātarkāḷem mātipāṟ</l>
<l>pēṇinumpi ṟappeṉumpi ṇakkaṟukka kiṟṟirē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O people who, thinking [them] as refuge, [seek] support and live by taking refuge</l>
<l>In gods without the power to give boons even when worshipped by</l>
<l>people with a bad appearance when looked at and by those whose reputation</l>
<l rend="indent">is not sweet to the ears!</l>
<l>Are you able to sever your bondage of  births worshipping our Cause?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
